comment: World Peace (LAL) makes incidental contact with Wiggins (MIN) that does not affect his FOM.

Randle (LAL) and Towns (MIN) briefly engage and separate in the post.
Nance Jr. (LAL) makes incidental contact with Towns (MIN) during rebounding.
Nance Jr. (LAL) makes marginal contact with Rubio (MIN) during the loose ball.
Randle (LAL) and Towns (MIN) briefly engage and separate in the post.

World Peace (LAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Wiggins (MIN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Russell (LAL) sets the screen on Towns (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Dieng (MIN) enters the paint area prior to the free throw being released.
Towns (MIN) makes contact with Randle (LAL) that affects his SQBR on the driving shot attempt.
